name: Giving names
description:
Artdiogen Gallery presents. A picture mystery that brings happiness.

What is named, exists,
And Light has named itself in everything.
In many different languages we know the common beginning of the conversation - the Name.
And with a name the magnet inside suddenly begins to feel that the spirit of the native has stepped towards us in our common home.

Who does a person give a name to? What kind of names are they? What do these different names have in common? What is their journey? Together? Separately?
These are but a few simple questions that cannot be answered by staying the same. 
At the very least, let's remember that cockroaches in our heads, and even more so demons, are much easier to deal with if we don't give them names.
